1
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:02,560
We're heading out.

2
00:00:02,560 --> 00:00:04,480
Make sure to lock up.

3
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:05,480
Take care.

4
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:10,720
Hi-na-ta!

5
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:11,720
I have a bad feeling about this.

6
00:00:14,840 --> 00:00:15,920
What is it?

7
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:18,080
I'm busy.

8
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:20,640
Huh?

9
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:23,160
Does this mean...

10
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:25,720
A peaceful life,

11
00:00:25,720 --> 00:00:27,080
is finally back?

12
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:29,880
Thank goodness!

13
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:31,640
Achoo!

14
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:34,600
Here, take a tissue.

15
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:36,040
Oh, thanks.

16
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:42,360
You don't want to catch a cold.

17
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:50,280
I made you some hot cocoa.

18
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,080
What's with you?

19
00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:03,360
What do you mean, what's with me?

20
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:04,480
Stop staring at me.

21
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,440
I can't help it.

22
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,600
We live together, it's bound to happen.

23
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:12,160
No, it's not just seeing me.

24
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,320
You're clearly just staring at me.

25
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,640
What did you say?

26
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,000
This guy...

27
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,000
He's so annoying.

28
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,360
I really want to kick him out.
